{"tid":1453904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[士氣增益] 默念：有臥底都好，前線行動再升級都好，不割蓆，不篤魁，不責難。","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:22:33.000Z","uid":295300,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4c0eb5160bc84fb7d18f702a3b929ad0d78ae84f","tid":1453904,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:39:16.000Z","msg":"默念：有臥底都好，前線行動再升級都好，不割蓆，不篤魁，不責難。佢哋係一班有覺悟嘅人，押上生命同前途嘅人，當然會希望佢哋安全平安，但做咩我哋控制唔到，只能支持。<br />\n<br />\n若果你今日用警察扮示威者一下將過去義士嘅所作所為推落警察度，滿足到嘅只有你廉價嘅道德潔癖，但日後義士再昇級就會處處受到制肘，更有冒上被指控係鬼嘅風險。實然上係割緊蓆。<br />\n<br />\n尋晚大家都好震撼好難過，今日去機場呢個 safe haven 取下暖無可厚非。但之後路要繼續行，亦要支持身邊嘅人繼續行。保重。"},{"pid":"a178085938f49249fa98197d132b4fe3106c61fe","tid":1453904,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:39:50.000Z","msg":"有緣睇到就睇<br />\n自推十次"},{"pid":"28f9ba9e1a94b371a2d6627b4be28e2e2d0c0d8f","tid":1453904,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6dea453c12d53cc1711f9f6259dcaf2e284efc","tid":1453904,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6f9e08bac811efafb931b8787c576ae0207011","tid":1453904,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de321bea9389f8aa54afe962c8dc4b022f42a026","tid":1453904,"uid":295300,"